         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne 19 March [18]96 ¶ editorial addition. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you that His Excellency the Governor in Council has been pleased to order that your services ¶  ¶ as Government B...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">96.03.19</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Charles Topp</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No.15, p. 190, unit 109, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office of Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 19 March [18]96<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition</seg>.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you that His Excellency the Governor in Council has been pleased to order that your services<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>as Government Botanist be retained in the Public Service until the 30th June next.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>It was a requirement for the continued employment of officers<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>aged<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>60<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and above<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that the Givernment<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>certify<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the service of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the officer was essential and seek the approval of the Governor in Council. M had last been renewed to 31<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>March 1896, see W. Callaway to M, 4<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>January 1896.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Charles A. Topp</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Sir Ferdinand von Mueller K.C.M.G. &amp;c.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Government Botanist</p>
         </div>
      </body>
